author: vanbesien
body:
To explain: For a long time (5 years) we had two configurations running:
FED and FEDTest. At was not really documented and nobody really knew
what it was. It seemed that FED was broken an FEDTest was showing
useful stuff. So recently we rectified this situation by making FED the
real working and fixed one, meaning that FEDTest should stop existing
and should be removed.

(Note: This is not super urgent, it's just something that should not be forgotten)
title: Removed old and obsolete fedtest config 80X
